<a data-tip="p$t$kaiserwang730" href="/people/kaiserwang730">Kaiser</a>，<strong title="天亮了" class="zu-question-my-bio">天亮了</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="522">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yi-yiyi-6-95" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yi-yiyi-6-95" class="zg-link" title="伊一伊">伊一伊</a>、</span><span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$dai-bing-63-85" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/dai-bing-63-85" class="zg-link" title="戴兵">戴兵</a>、</span><span class="user-block">知乎用户</span>
</span>


<a href="javascript:;" class="more"> 等人赞同</a>


</div>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="3127781" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">中华儿女多奇志，不爱红装爱武装。<br><br>少女啊，你面带微笑，手拿菜刀，想必也是一抹醉人的风景。<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic2.zhimg.com/3d060e6ef78abb1dd2199df71021e52d_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="300" class="content_image" width="300"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="300" data-rawheight="300" class="content_image lazy" width="300" data-actualsrc="//pic2.zhimg.com/3d060e6ef78abb1dd2199df71021e52d_b.jpg"><br><br>我不禁想象了一下，你扔下菜刀，惊呼间双手托住粉腮的可人模样。<br>用佟掌柜的话讲：美得很，美得很。<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/10058713ed5c8ca1c9c02ed1202357db_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="1280" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/10058713ed5c8ca1c9c02ed1202357db_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="1280" data-rawheight="720" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="1280" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/10058713ed5c8ca1c9c02ed1202357db_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/10058713ed5c8ca1c9c02ed1202357db_b.jpg"><br>遥想当年昭烈帝，一进孙夫人的门，也曾教那满屋的刀枪剑戟斧钺钩叉拐子流星，吓尿了裤子。<br>但后来生活不还是非常的愉悦，传为一段佳话。<br><br>我观你这男友，往高了说有点枭雄的种，往低了讲是个生活的靠。<br>过日子嘛，不外乎就是多喝热水早点睡，哪有那些个枫丹白露翡冷翠。<br><br>今日菜刀在手，何时缚住老公？<br>你就嫁了吧。


</div>

